# Git Hub Steps

// this command will create local copy of the repository on your machine
git clone [repository_url]

// checks if there is any changes made in the repository
git status

// add all the changes in a stage package
git add .

// gives a name to everything staged so far and prepare it to be send to the remote repo
git commit -am "[custom_message_describing_the_changes]"

// will push all the commits done so far
git push
